This place is really good, when I first ordered chicken rice from them for home delivery, I wasn't very happy with what came. The rice was all drenched in white sauce and it really ruined the taste of the rice and chicken. However the second time I ordered, I specified to leave out the white sauce and just put salad. This time the rice was really good and me and my whole family fell in love with their food, especially the rice. I suggest you ask for the chicken rice without white sauce and salad because then they put more rice and chicken to fill the space in the box. You can get more rice for what you will pay if you do this. Just a tip. I haven't tried all the other food from there, but the French fries and mozzarella sticks are not bad and the burgers are pretty good sized. Happy eating 😌✊
